    a: "<p>The shield becomes charged with lightning and has a <span class=\"d3-color-green\">25%</span> chance to Stun the first enemy hit for <span class=\"d3-color-green\">2</span> seconds. Each enemy hit after the first has a <span class=\"d3-color-green\">5%</span> reduced chance to be Stunned.</p> <p class=\"subtle\">Unlocked at level <em>24</em></p>",
    b: "<p>The shield erupts in flames and has a <span class=\"d3-color-green\">33%</span> chance to explode on impact, dealing <span class=\"d3-color-green\">310%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class=\"d3-color-green\">10</span> yards.</p> <p class=\"subtle\">Unlocked at level <em>29</em></p>",
    c: "<p>When the shield hits an enemy, your Armor is increased by <span class=\"d3-color-green\">5%</span> and Life regeneration is increased by <span class=\"d3-color-green\">5%</span> for <span class=\"d3-color-green\">4</span> seconds.</p> <p class=\"subtle\">Unlocked at level <em>38</em></p>",
